Python is an interpreted language which means that the written code is not actually translated to a computer-readable format at run time.
Python is a high-level,object-oriented programming language which is another way to say that it can be used for nearly everything.
Python has wide range of applications from web and app development.
The syntax of the phyton language is clean and length of the code is relatively short.
Compared to other programming languages,it allows more run time flexibility.
For building large applications phython can be compiled to byte-code.
Python language is used in most of the companies like GOOGLE,YOUTUBE,IBM,......
 
